OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,FThe Theatre Royal Plymouth has been
OL,7,Fawarded more than #8 million in
OL,8,Fgovernment funding to help open up
OL,9,Faccess to its facilities, complete
OL,10,Fbuilding works, and upgrade its
OL,11,Ftechnologies.
OL,13,FThe Creative Foundations fund has been
OL,14,Fdesigned to protect 130 English
OL,15,Fcultural assets, like theatre venues,
OL,16,Fmuseums and libraries.
OL,18,FThe Plymouth site last underwent a
OL,19,Frefurbishment in 2013 - since then,
OL,20,Fmore than 3.5 million people have come
OL,21,Fthrough its doors.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
