OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,FThe award recognises the importance of
OL,7,FTheatre Royal Plymouth as a 'cultural
OL,8,Fpillar' of the South West and the
OL,9,Flevel of renovation needed to ensure
OL,10,Fit can remain open in the future.
OL,12,FThe Theatre said the investment would
OL,13,Fallow it to begin addressing some of
OL,14,Fits most pressing infrastructure needs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
