PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,FJames Mackenzie-Blackman, Chief
OL,7,FExecutive and Artistic Director at
OL,8,FTheatre Royal Plymouth, said: "This
OL,9,Ffunding is an incredible vote of
OL,10,Fconfidence in what Theatre Royal
OL,11,FPlymouth means to our city and the
OL,12,Fwider region.
OL,14,F"Our building has been a home for
OL,15,Fmillions of people, some discovering
OL,16,Ftheatre for the very first time,
OL,17,Fothers returning again and again.
OL,26,@pD@_OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
