CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,F"It has always been about more than
OL,7,Fbricks and mortar; it's about
OL,8,Fcreativity, connection and shared
OL,9,Fexperiences.
OL,11,FHe added: "This investment allows us
OL,12,Fto protect what makes this place so
OL,13,Fspecial, while reimagining what it can
OL,14,Fbe for generations to come."
OL,26,@vD@\O]
