OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,FCulture Secretary, Lisa Nandy said: "I
OL,7,Fwant everyone, everywhere to feel a
OL,8,Fsense of pride about where they come
OL,9,Ffrom. Cultural organisations across
OL,10,Fthe South West are important
OL,11,Fcustodians of local identity and play
OL,12,Fa key role in the story we tell
OL,13,Fourselves as a nation.
OL,26,@nD@eOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
