OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,F"Our Arts Everywhere Fund is
OL,7,Fdelivering on our commitment to
OL,8,Fsupport cultural assets across the
OL,9,Fcountry, increasing access and
OL,10,Fpreserving them for future
OL,11,Fgenerations. This is demonstrated by
OL,12,Fgrants announced today that will
OL,13,Fbenefit twelve culture venues,
OL,14,Fmuseums, and library services across
OL,15,Fthe South West.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
