CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,F"Arts and culture are the beating
OL,7,Fhearts of our communities, they have
OL,8,Fthe power to unite us in the face of
OL,9,Fdivision and break down barriers to
OL,10,Fopportunity. We want to harness the
OL,11,Fpower to help us build a brighter
OL,12,Ffuture for the people of the South
OL,13,FWest."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
