PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,FPhil Gibby, Area Director, Arts
OL,7,FCouncil England, said: "Today's
OL,8,Fannouncement marks a powerful
OL,9,Fcommitment to the cultural life of the
OL,10,FSouth West. I'm thrilled to confirm
OL,11,Fover #20 million of investment across
OL,12,F18 organisations, including #4 million
OL,13,Ffor museums and libraries.
OL,26,@oD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
