PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,F"This support will safeguard
OL,7,Fmuchloved venues, from major
OL,8,Fgalleries and civic museums to
OL,9,Fcommunity hubs, heritage sites and
OL,10,Fproducing theatres. It's about far
OL,11,Fmore than buildings ` it's about
OL,12,Fenabling artists, audiences and
OL,13,Fcommunities to thrive, because
OL,14,Fcreativity enriches all of our lives."
OL,16,FThe fund, provided by the Department
OL,17,Ffor Culture, Media and Sport and Arts
OL,18,FCouncil England, is worth a total of
OL,19,F#130 million - and will be split
OL,20,Fbetween 130 venues.
OL,26,@vD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
