PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,FThe particular fund supporting the
OL,7,FTheatre Royal Plymouth is the Creative
OL,8,FFoundations Fund, which has allocated
OL,9,F#96 million to 74 arts and cultural
OL,10,Fvenues to help theatres, performing
OL,11,Farts venues, galleries and grassroots
OL,12,Fmusic venues address urgent
OL,13,Finfrastructure needs.
OL,15,FVenues across the South West that will
OL,16,Fbenefit from this fund:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
