PN,43611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776280294
OL,3,CArts venues across South West awarded
OL,4,Cmoney to 'protect English assets'
OL,6,FAs well as this, Bristol Museums has
OL,7,Fbeen awarded #3,567,713 from the
OL,8,FMuseum Estate and Development Fund - a
OL,9,Fpot of #25.5 million to support 28
OL,10,Fmuseums to undertake vital
OL,11,Finfrastructure works, and improve the
OL,12,Fvisitor experience.
OL,14,FDevon County Council is set to receive
OL,15,F#200,000 and South Gloucestershire
OL,16,FCouncil's Cultural Services will be
OL,17,Fawarded #167,639 as part of the
OL,18,FLibraries Improvement Fund.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
